verilator-4.038

> testcase

```verilog
// t_consthi.v
module t(reg_i, reg_o);

input           reg_i;
output          reg_o;

wire [1:0]      reg_i;
reg  [1049:0]   reg_o;

always @ (*) begin
    if (reg_i[1] == 1'b1)
        reg_o = {986'd0, 64'hffff0000ffff0000};
    else if (reg_i[0] == 1'b1)
        reg_o = {64'hffff0000ffff0000, 986'd0};
    else
        reg_o = 1050'd0;
end

endmodule
```

